373
00:21:57,370 --> 00:21:58,060
How is it?

374
00:22:01,610 --> 00:22:02,540
It tastes pretty good.

375
00:22:04,180 --> 00:22:05,020
Really?

376
00:22:06,060 --> 00:22:08,449
I need to compliment her.

