414
00:24:14,940 --> 00:24:16,019
Yang Shanshan.

415
00:24:16,020 --> 00:24:17,940
Some luck you have.

416
00:24:28,900 --> 00:24:29,540
Thank you.

417
00:24:38,450 --> 00:24:39,130
Friday.

