00:25:02,130 --> 00:25:03,580
So this is Friday.

425
00:25:04,450 --> 00:25:07,539
She can work and
communicate like a human?

426
00:25:07,540 --> 00:25:10,059
Friday is great, okay?

427
00:25:10,060 --> 00:25:10,700
Friday.

