00:25:26,450 --> 00:25:27,489
Mr. Si.

431
00:25:27,490 --> 00:25:32,250
Si Jiali, 26 years old,
Master's special assistant.

432
00:25:37,130 --> 00:25:39,490
"Jiali" as in "to start and family
