452
00:26:17,940 --> 00:26:18,849
Got it.

453
00:26:18,850 --> 00:26:19,940
You may go.

454
00:26:21,130 --> 00:26:22,060
Before that...

455
00:26:23,090 --> 00:26:23,970
Friday.

