503
00:28:53,580 --> 00:28:54,250
I don't see anyone.

504
00:28:55,130 --> 00:28:56,450
You really are pretty interesting.

505
00:28:57,090 --> 00:28:58,699
Look, it's so great when you smile like that.

506
00:28:58,700 --> 00:28:59,820
